HEADWORD: Intercolonial
<hw>In`ter*co*lo"ni*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Between or
among colonies; pertaining to the intercourse or mutual relations of
colonies; <as>as, <ex>intercolonial</ex> trade</as>.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>In`ter*co*lo"ni*al*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

